<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_355" id="177r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_355_r1l1">Herman Hochprant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l2">ʒu Purelſwogen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_355_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hochprant / vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Jacob Topler vnſer burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l4">vvie Jr Jm ſein Armlewte cʒu Scheinbach gevangen vnd Jn ir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l5">habe genomen habt <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ Armleute ledig vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l6">Jn ir habe <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / Als etc / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc vnd het Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l7"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger ıcht <expan>cʒuſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> wollen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l8">vvir ew oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſcheimbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalte <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l9">ſleunigs rechten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen vvenn vvir des ermant vverden ſo derſelb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l10">vnſer <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim iſt / Het Jr aber cʒu <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Armleute<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l11">
<del rend="strikethrough">dıe Jr <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd das Jr <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt </del> / ıcht <expan>cʒuſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l12">vvil Er ew 
<del rend="strikethrough">dan </del> auch cʒum rehten ſtellen / do Er das <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> tun ſol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_355_r1l13">vnd lat vns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> vvıder wıſſen <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_355" id="177r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herman Hochprant zu Purelswogen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hochprant, uns hat
                            <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Jacob Topler, unser burger, wie ir im
                        sein armlewte czu Scheinbach gevangen und in ir habe genomen habt.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> armleute ledig und in ir habe
                                <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het ir
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger icht
                            <expan>czusprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
                        wollen wir ew oder <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheimbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> sleunigs rechten
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen, wenn wir des ermant werden, so
                        derselb unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ist. Het ir aber czu
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>armleute<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>czu sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        die wil er ew auch czum rehten stellen, do er das
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> tun sol. Und lat uns des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wissen.
                        <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
